data.description: Awesome Edmond home for sale in the DEER CREEK SCHOOL DISTRICT!!! Great location! Home has 4 bedrooms and 2 baths with high ceilings, granite countertops, custom stained cabinetry. Nice sized backyard and storm shelter in the 2 car garage. 2 Neighborhood pools, parks and sports court!! Schedule your showing today! Serious inquiries only. Property is leased until 7/31/2024 at $2095 buyer will have to sign a property management agreement with Homeworx until lease ends. 24 hour notice and proof of funds or pre approval letter is required to show.
